Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優秀的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦參與戰鬥就似乎不得不背負相對的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都說撫子是地球聯合軍中最優秀的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我們才會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"機動戰艦"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著痛苦所踢起的小石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若反彈回來也會變成鑽石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到手的夢想不算是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請堅信它一定會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡從不氣餒的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想哭的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠永遠在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的方式驕傲地去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去熱衷的日子是夢的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU GET BURNINC
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那碎片收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能看見以明天為目標的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOING YOUR DAY'S GROW UP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:01:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在聯合軍前頭的撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:02:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也被敵軍當成殺父仇人般集中攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然對方不肯罷休我們也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底地幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家的興亡就全靠我們的奮鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS全機都已出動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的混帳蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部攻擊都是從撫子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS隊連友軍也攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊友軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊誘導裝置沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子的AESTIVALIS全都在攻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人，敵人是那邊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子的AESTIVALIS\N正在對敵軍與聯合軍雙方進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼，攻擊停止停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在極近距離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在停止攻擊的話我方會全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，攻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要攻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是打算攻擊敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎麼會變成這樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子本身沒有受到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之\N各人照顧好自己出動支援的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有駕駛員了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輔佐艦長，這是副官的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不光是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要保護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純，請回答，純
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天的戰鬥真是亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方也被不分敵我攻擊的撫子搞迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草草中止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想被捲入撫子不明原因的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍也撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何大家平安無事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS也幾乎只有擦傷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，這個太過份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純，為什麼你要上去?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，你想說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是手語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說\N在人手不足的撫子上這是身為副官的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雖然很好\N可是要上去時要穿飛行裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了百合香，他說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是為了百合香穿上飛行裝也比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今，我不想跟你囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，別多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛AESTIVALIS的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要繫上安全帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好脖子傷得不嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過暫時無法好好說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時不能說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常都只有對百合香的愛語但卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純，加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為沒人傷亡就高興得太早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這戰艦一艘多少錢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我打下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘毛地黃比撫子更貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打下了五十架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就光而言很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話每一架都有聯合軍的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說只是也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說我的擊落數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共78架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵我兩方加起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,62架是我方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人你從剛才就都不出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒大家那麼慘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打算攻擊敵軍的鬱金香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是毀的卻是聯合軍的燃料基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，你知道那基地的建設費嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些不是都有保險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是至少要花慰問金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我方無人傷亡真是奇跡般地幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問金要再增加的話真不知要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一名腦震盪後遺症的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，最主要的原因是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會攻擊聯合軍呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是故意去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們所愛的是綠色的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕不可能背叛聯合軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說是整備不良了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話我可不能當做沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我們的安全整備有漏洞是不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過連日的戰鬥多少都會有些失誤不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修部門的疲勞度也不容忽視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管疲勞不疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備失敗是會出人命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整備的好壞關係著生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然在女人方面失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是機械的整備我絕不會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把你們的疏失都怪到我們頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員或整備士都沒有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，為了查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍的調查團正朝我們這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一直嘮叨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是我們撫子的防衛攻擊電腦出了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，不要，那不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從調查船逃出的救生艇正在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，又有攻擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰下的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打，那個不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容地球軍的調查船救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撫子誤射的調查員們不可能冷靜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片面指責撫子的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之說別人壞話是最輕鬆的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我說，電腦有學習機能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會根據經驗進行學習採取最妥善的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子的電腦它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是"思兼"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是電腦的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給只不過是道具的電腦取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是二十世紀末的惡習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是思兼就是思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是重鍾還是輕鍾都無所謂\N(音同思兼)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之撫子的電腦中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過去突破防線的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N它已經把聯合軍是妨礙撫子行動的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段記憶學起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此與地球聯合軍共同作戰會產生抗拒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打個比方來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是被競爭對手吸收合併
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做牛做馬的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個比喻真簡單易懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，我瞭解，我瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作壓力累積過多的話人是會崩潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的話則會進入凍結狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只是凍結的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把變成Bug的資料消掉再重新設定就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼具有自動重新設定功能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這電腦所學的對聯合軍的敵對意識太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次重新設定就會增加壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終至演變成像這次的攻擊行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決的方法就是完全消除學習記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後改寫新的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣隨隨便便可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子好不容易到火星所學到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與敵人戰鬥的有效率的對應記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會被完全消除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子是屬於聯合軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單獨行動時的記憶有百害而無一利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為保衛地球而戰的是人類不是機器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說，撫子是在聯合軍旗下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須忘掉與聯合軍敵對的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉就是徹底捨去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是大人的藉口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自己不利的事情只要忘掉就好的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們都太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…怎麼每個人打扮都是一樣的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"撫子電腦控制室"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切換成由副電腦管制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,INSTALL開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不消除所有的資料就不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改寫讓思兼絕對服從的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子從此就脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 從民用船變成真正的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為軍方工作的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼，百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻煩你跟我來一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有放棄當廚師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰以外的時間我要練習作菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我需要AESTIVALIS的駕駛員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找誰都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像涼子啦，光，泉，甚至赤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得是天河不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都是這樣子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:12:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制室都被佔據了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣危險的事又不能在艦橋做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…小心點 那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我辛苦作的人型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡可以做嗎?除蟲什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外表不怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經跟思兼連線過不知幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式作得很好，看了也不會膩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可進入思兼的程式之內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查有問題的地方或修改
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂電腦空間的必殺掃除人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼，對我的興趣有意見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟我的主電腦連線然後操控摸擬器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會變成頂尖的電腦戰士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河AESTI啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在電腦裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被我影像化的電腦記憶中樞印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來這是參照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失敗七次的麻省理工學院圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該往哪裡走呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右轉，直走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是思兼的自主意識部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是正在覆蓋中的新的軍方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，幹掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在攻擊新程式的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,INSTALL會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子會和以前一樣繼續反抗地球軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先往前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去思兼的自主意識部份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不太忍心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好善良，天河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼的自主意識部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的撫子身為撫子的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己確定自己存在的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己存在的證明?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的重要的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了的重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶…回憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘記也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就是自己的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他稍微忘掉一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他忘記?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個伸出來的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把那部份剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過枝芽還會再長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天思兼會記起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後撫子不會改變自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼，稍微忘卻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後長大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 你只要假裝服從聯合軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫子仍然還是撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼出來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的異物排除意識
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是思兼的自衛反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想忘記重要記憶的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼人3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是思兼輸入的資料中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強，最正確的，正義的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他當成是自己的夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為思兼和你一起看過激鋼人的錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也用不著變成激鋼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為最瞭解激鋼人的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要我跟激鋼人戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把激鋼人什麼的幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，請戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方似乎不想放過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼飛切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，打不過他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是激鋼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會贏的，天河一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那個機器人的思念應該比思兼更強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…思念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼飛踢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣分不出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，由人來操縱我方比較不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為人類的天河\N對那機器人從很久以前就非常瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直喜愛著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人的思念是不可能輪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的話真讓我高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很久以前，一直喜愛著...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激鋼人從第十七集開始換成激鋼人V
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的變形模式!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍鋼人你知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自衛反應消滅記憶修正完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河 剩的下只有盡快解決新程式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去一切都會被消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些傢伙發現的話就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛就對調查團的電腦灌入假資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管放手幹吧，明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍鋼人只有設定資料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒出現在電視上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有在凱的設定專輯裡看過而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河的信念真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來，撫子的電腦，思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還有撫子自身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表面沒有發現任何異狀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利順利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球會贏的，這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎?艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前進，右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前進，右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"那忘不了的日子"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"現在為此而活著"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:21:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有純粹的情感沈睡其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要追尋夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容與淚水的數目就會漸漸增多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時想要更像自我地去感受風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於其他人的我自己的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿速度感心跳加速的冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當明人離開百合香的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛構與現實的分界崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖，厲害，嘔心瀝血的傑作終於誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿精彩動作的絢爛豪華大作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻給全國的好孩子及媽媽們的豪華貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在職場，學校，家庭獨佔話題的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，機動戰艦撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"真實"不是只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看喲
